values:
Man o man.

These past few entrees just ... aren't ME! It's like ... I'm usually so happy but IDK lately .Ugh.

I'm so ... tired.mad.stressed.disapointed. Mostly disapointed. IDK It's just I'm so sick of things not working out ... like something goes wrong and it's like ... why did I even bother getting excited. Ugh. So pissed off!

So Busch Gardens Friday ... !!! I'm so excited but like I wanted more people to come like I wanted Josh to come and Justin might come if he looses his game tonight lol But right now it's just the original guys ... Marino Cass Charlie Coley n Me Sessa *Marinos bud* too. That's cool and all but ... I'm kinda like ... trying to branch out a little ... please DON'T take that the way it sounds ... I love those guys but I wanted like others to come too! I mean last summer we had them ... lol

I'm so mad. Haha. I failed a bio test and school just sucks! Plus some lady in the Cool Taste place (BEST SMOOTHIES) said she thought I was in middle school ... okay. No. lol The other day some lady thought I was a 11th grader ... I'm like common lady do I look like I'm 12? lmao NO! Ugh ...

Sorry I'm so grochy! I'm just soooooooooo mad! I'm sick of people changing !!!! It's like last week things were fine and now it's like ASSHOLE WEEK! Let's see who can be the biggest aword! :) I know someone who would win! lol Ugh !

Anyway ... tonight I have a stupid chorus concert which I just don't want to do and tons of HW I hate life right now!

What happend to the old days man !? Well they're over.

I need to get away.

</3 Moa

Let's go back to the days when Marino & Cass sang that in Mr. Brown's ! THOSE were the effing days!

Happy Cinco de mayo! (Did I mention I HATE SPANISH CLASS! lol)

So wow!

It's been awhile ...

This is one of the entries ... where I just babble on about shit that wont even be an issue tomorrow (Haha!)

I miss :

Not caring, not knowing anything, getting sun-burnt, acting dumb, lighting things on fire, laughing at stupid stuff, sleepovers, stayin up all night talking about BOYS, going on the boat, lame school-dances, putting quotes in my info from retarded people, having inside jokes that made no sence and you forgot about like a week later, laughing till I cry, not being so intense, not taking things so seriously, being laid-back, listening to Jimmy Buffet, drawing, coloring, playing video games, looking up retarded stuff online, talking to buds on the phone forever about dumb stuff, riding a bike, jumping on D's trampoline, running around, climbing trees, playing g.i joes (haha dork), building sand-castles, playing cards, watching the history ch. (lmao riiight), being annoyed, boy meets world, SUMMER, rollercoasters, cotten candy, drinkin too many sodas and bouncing off the walls, being hyper, doin things my mom wouldn't agree with, bein sneaky, walks, poptarts, Marino playin Solcom for days on end, eatin popcorn, watchin movies with friends, having bon-fires, camping, going on trips/vacations, the keys, the beach, TUBING, the cruise (last summer), my cousins/other family, quoting stupid movies, playin computer games, going out of my way to see a hott guy, havin crushes on people, mr.brown's lectures that everyone got pissed about, reading those stupid books, 8th grade (parts), watching a boy chase my car down his street (ha), hating someone so much you love them, liking the guy and him liking you back right away, not thinking, singing to songs in the radio and thinkin about how much I miss Maryland people (haha that's u Matt), being online being my life, working out everyday, P.E. (8th grade), going to people's houses on the weekends, tanning, Coley and I going one place to the next on bike rides, Seein the lil kids at the middle school with Coley, talking to my cousins, seeing them, jammin to Bob Marley, school not bein so hard, hangin posters of boy bands on my wall, singing along to NSYNC and BSB, walking along the beach telling Coley how much I liked whoever I was with, smiling all the time, playin in the rain, playin tag and hideNseek, ghost stories, Are You Afraid of the Dark?, candles, insence, swimming, volleyball/one-bounce ...

Basically all the old shit I used to do and love ... lol It just seems to dull now.

I know I know ... drama queen over here but seriously dudes. I'm just like common! I want some fun and goofyness in my llife again! I'm so sick of everyone (including myself) being so DOWN and just not having too much fun ... Believe me I'm happy I just want some more fun dumb stuff! I want it back! Not everything. I mean I'm SO happy things are the way they are just a little formatted is what I'm asking for! Haha!

Well ... I guess I'm out. Math HW calls! Oh and I still like the same person like ... I'm crazy about him BUT IDK there are some other guys out there so ... who knows ;)! <3 hehe

Latta gattas -Em-

Never forget the times when your young and stupid ... These are the days of our lives so don't take 'em for granted!

The words of someone I used to know.

lol That sounds so "abuh" but truthfully I'm alright :)

I just ... well It's hard.

I am in such a pensive mood. Very deep thought. Blah!

Sooo many people have changed (some for the good; others for the worst) and it's sad because I've been so close to everyone! I just hate to loose anything.

I am doing great though! I went to Britt's house with Coley Friday night and had a BLAST! It was nice to be somewhere else for a change! It was funny because on Monday I finally talked to Cody Rogers (I used to know him in 6th grade) and all of a sudden I was at his party on Friday! It was too funny!

Saturday Coley and I got up from Britt's and went on da boat! It was fun but it was cloudy/windy so we had to come in early. Still got a tan though :)!

FINALLY got my new phone! I am so happy! It's sweet ... it was easier cuz Coley and I always like to talk on the phone and now I can talk with the speaker ... Haha!! Easily amused right huuurr!

So overall the weekend was fun and today Coley and I went on a 3 mile walk! It was nice to get the exersize AND get out! lol I love walkin!

I am the type of person who totally lives in the past ... and I hate it. I always get so sad and like sentimental! I need to just CHILL OUT and enjoy life! lol Which anyone who knows me ... knows I totally do enjoy life and most the time I am super happy but sometimes I just get so ... down. lol Who doesn't though??? Yepp!

So life is good right now! I am stoked about so much and Summer is almost here! What could be better???

Well .

lol I guess I'm gonna go! My C.D. has ended and I hate the silence! Gotta change it! Haha!

Latta gattas!

lmao. I know dorky song but ... it's like IDK it says stuff like the lyrics! lol Read closely! ;)

Let's just start off by saying ...

I should be studying. lol

But since when do I study? Seriously 4th quarter I never do any work! I hate that ...

Ne ways on to cool stuff ...

I am so happy! Those last two entries were like WHOA but it's all good now!

Wooo!!!

The best feeling in the world ...

Knowing you can remember every detail and feeling ... but letting it all go at the same time!

Life is good.

So I decided I want a boyfriend afterall lol! Wasn't planning on finishing the year off with a man but IDK got my eye out for someone ;) Noooobody knows who it is and I'm gonna keep it that way ... at least for now. IDK what I want but I know I like him. I love unexpected stuff!!!

Did I mention I am extremely happy???

I made a movie today of the past and I'm working on one about my lil sista Coley and I! It's so fun! lol I love finding shit on your computer you didn't know ya had!

Wow ... some stuff just CRACKS ME UP!

What's funny is I feel like crying because of IT but IT is funny at the same time.

I hate change. lol No matter how HAPPY I am ... I still hate it. Ohhh well ... that's life!

I just wish I could go back and say some shit to SOOO many people ... maybe then just maybe things would be different.

But there's no more Summer ... and this Summer aint gonna be like last Summer. At all.
